					   <td>

			
			
			



<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
<tr>
	<td width="1%">&nbsp;</td>
	<td width="98%">
  
		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%">
		<tr>
		    <td valign="top">
		     <p><font face="Verdana" size="3"><b>Article Title:</b>&nbsp;</font>
		     <font face="Verdana" size="2"><b>Verant Announces New Character Transfer Service</b></font><br>
		     <a href = "../Subscribe.asp?DID=462898" ><font face="Verdana" size="2">[Subscribe to this document]</font></a></p>
			 </td>
		</tr>
		
		<tr><td>&nbsp;</tr><tr>
		
		    <td valign="top"><div style= "padding:4;float: right"> <script language=JavaScript src=http://www.obsidian-tech.com/absolutebm/abmx.aspx?z=26></script></div><p><font face="Verdana" size="2">
		    <blockquote>
Players who have wished, dreamed, and hoped for the ability to move characters between servers without the use of a /movelog server split are now graced with the ability to do so. 
<br><br>
Those wishing to take advantage of this offer should also realize that you lose items and coin upon the transfer. While this may be a good offer, keep in mind that it is for a limited time only! So, if you want to transfer, now is the time to do it!
<br><br>
Details regarding the new plan may be found <a href="https://store.station.sony.com/eq_char_moves/index.jsp">here</a>. 
</blockquote>
		    </font></p>
			 </td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
		     <td valign="top">
		     <br><font face="Verdana" size="2"><b><a href="UserUpdate.asp?id=462898">[Add Comments] Please Add your comments here!</a></b></font><br><hr>
			  </td>
		</tr>

		</table>

	</td>
	<td width="1%">&nbsp;</td>
</tr>
