				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				I'm going to basically say this:  I've done the move, and more importantly, it was the right thing for me.<BR>
<BR>
I took a character I spent months playing on a server different from where my RL friends were playing on.  He's 40.  I lost about 12kp worth of items during the move.  But before the move was done, I did something rather cool.  I gave my stuff away, and all my money.  I gave it all to newbies, a few friends who desired certain items, and even gave my paw of opolla to some guy who wanted to buy it.<BR>
<BR>
I didn't want to quit the character.  I figure the price, and knowing that all I have to really do is TP people around, buy my stuff back, or even quest for it again.  It's all because I wanted to have my high level character with my RL friends.<BR>
<BR>

