				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				   To all the whiners SHUT UP and stop playing the game.  You are like the little kids in the playground who take their ball just because they dont like the game, only in this game the ball belongs to Verant.  <BR>
   Character transfers were never part of the game, it was understood that when you start your character you keep it on that server, that is why there is an option to pick servers.  Now because of many VALID request from customers eg..families playing on one account now able to afford a new computer, the request were made for those customers.  This was done for awhile, believe it or not for FREE!  Then as the word spread, it was made available to the general population.  So Verant allows it.  But believe me they dont want to do it, that is why the price is pretty high, to act as a deterent.  It is not high to make money (although they will) but high to lessen the demand. <BR>
   There will always be people who will try to get around policy to benefit them.  A new breed of ebayers will come out of this.  And  I will predict that there will be another policy change because THOSE people will to say the least will F*CK it up for the people that this move was intended for.  But for all you whiners- just quit the game, if all you have to do is whine about it, then its just plain stupid to play a game that you dont enjoy.  SUCK it up.
				</font>
			</td>

